nhc_headline: ...GABRIELLE EXPECTED TO BECOME A HURRICANE ON SUNDAY... ...FORECAST TO PASS EAST OF BERMUDA ON MONDAY...
summary: ...GABRIELLE EXPECTED TO BECOME A HURRICANE ON SUNDAY... ...FORECAST TO PASS EAST OF BERMUDA ON MONDAY... As of 11:00 PM AST Sat Sep 20 the center of Gabrielle was located near 26.3, -59.2 with movement NNW at 9 mph. The minimum central pressure was 996 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
